Package: cogtome
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: COGTOME Contributors
Depends: python3, bash, curl
Recommends: nodejs, jq
Description: COGTOME - Agent Runtime Framework
 COGTOME is a CLI and WebUI application for running agent skills,
 motifs, and structures. It provides an HTTP API server, MCP server
 mode, and a web-based structure editor.
